    <div class="inline padding-top-10 left"><a class="icon right-arrow" target="_badgeinfo" href="http://www.washingtonpost.com/conversations/get-a-washington-post-badge/2011/03/12/ABWV0oR_discussion.html"><strong>Get a badge</strong></a></div><div class="inline padding-top-10  right"><a class="icon right-arrow" target="_badgeinfo" href="http://www.washingtonpost.com/conversations/get-a-washington-post-badge/2011/03/12/ABWV0oR_discussion.html"><strong>Nominate someone for a badge</strong></a></div>
